origin_prompt.content:
你能够调用以下的API:
{'name': 'HousingFund.calculate_loan_amount', 'description': 'This function calculates the maximum loan amount based on income, employment history, and credit score.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'income', 'type': 'NUMBER', 'description': 'The monthly income of the applicant.'}, {'name': 'employment_years', 'type': 'NUMBER', 'description': 'The number of years the applicant has been employed.'}, {'name': 'credit_score', 'type': 'NUMBER', 'description': 'The credit score of the applicant.'}], 'return_data': [{'name': 'loan_amount', 'description': 'The calculated maximum loan amount.'}]}
请直接生成JSON格式的回复. 不要在回复中增加注释(//).

{
    // 你这一步的目标
    "目标": string;
    // 你要调用的API名称
    "名称": string;
    // 当前API的参数输入(JSON格式)
    "参数输入": Record<string, any>;
}
